          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1667899944191-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, drain your <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop your <strong>tofu</strong> into large bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped tofu</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>soy sauce </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and set aside to marinate</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1667899947447-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
