    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and slice (don't chop!) <strong>half </strong>your <strong>garlic cloves </strong>(save the rest for later!)</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
