      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu is crispy, add the <strong>onion wedges </strong>and <strong>chopped pepper </strong>to the pan with the <strong>sliced garlic </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and cook for 4-5 min further or until the vegetables are beginning to soften – this is your <strong>salt & pepper tofu</strong></p>",
