    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate the <strong>remaining garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated garlic </strong>with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong>, <strong>remaining sliced chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>dipping sauce</strong></p>",
